TEXT.S: Carmen Argenziano kawas tay 1943, ryax sa tay 27 nqu tay 10, Carmen Argenziano, squliq na Bunge'. qyanux ru mincyogun Carmen Argenziano htgan na ryax maki Sharon, Pennsylvania. m'rkays beh Sharpsville.cyugal laqi nha,sazing laqi mlikuy ru qutux laqi kneril qnyatan nya. semong nya balay ga Jacob Carter Selmak maki Stargate SG 1. wal mhuqil 2019 kawas 2 byacing 10 ryax(pitu pgan magan kawas minqyanux nya).
